title: Shoot Your Shot to Royce Da 5'9 Interview
itunes:title: Shoot Your Shot to Royce Da 5'9 Interview
description:
Tuesday 5/1 - Today on the show we had listeners call up for "Shoot Your Shot" and lets just say things that happen in the dark definitely come out in the light. Moreover, we had rapper Roycda 5'9 stop where he spoke about his music, new projects and more. Also, Charlamagne gave Jersery Shore member Ronnie "Donkey of the Day" because he got into a physical altercation with his girlfriend while live streaming.
